{"tid":1149821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【HPV疫苗】逾百內地客湧診所要求退款 環亞體檢報警","createTime":"2019-05-11T11:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T12:10:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b563fdf296fcc00b607b7f5df26f77ddada56633","tid":1149821,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190511/_2019051114095371835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190511%2F_2019051114095371835.jpg&h=f3caa3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環亞體檢集團被指供應水貨HPV九價疫苗，今午再有大批內地客到該集團位於佐敦的診所，追問疫苗真偽及要求退款，期間因人數太多，有職員報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n今早9時許，集團位於佐敦嘉賓商業大廈的診所外，已經有數名內地客等候開門。其後到場人數漸多，至中午12時許，已經有逾百人到場，場內水洩不通。有職員強調所有子宮頸癌疫苗均為默沙東藥廠生產，是真貨，但願意為顧客提供退款服務。不過現場亦有市民預約打第一針，但被拒絕，指現時沒有貨。<br />\n<br />\n現場人數眾多，部分人不滿鼓譟，期間有職員報警，數名衝鋒隊警員手持盾牌到場了解。<br />\n<br />\n環亞體檢集團早前發聲明指，公司所提供之疫苗均由默沙東藥廠生產，並以恰當方式運送儲存，符合最高質素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1498393/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1498393%2F&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=6e4019ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1498393%2F&h=132d9bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1498393/</a>"},{"pid":"c15d98f2922146faddf7007ab70c0efa67ab918a","tid":1149821,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"血濃於水...咁都做得出...失望！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247cd9356d22de28c5c267cfb1ad41817506ff9d","tid":1149821,"uid":3457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"退款？ 好呀 係體內抽返d野出黎味退比你囉 支那豬"},{"pid":"a3b621232e73c30096553090e9c0ff2d32a1a217","tid":1149821,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"打得咁辛苦返大陸打啦！去澳門都可以"},{"pid":"9ba034b24470f20290fdfd1a9be14a2eb45e729b","tid":1149821,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a6eb687961ccab7cb93fe3d35d23ea1979657b7","tid":1149821,"uid":217450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"打啲愛滋毒柒啲賤蟲就啱"},{"pid":"037f6d2c17e9bb8900f15fd49adf894600a2c211","tid":1149821,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"支持有關業界對中國人既打壓"},{"pid":"7ea37ecf5491aebe3a1634064a54b4e0c0a0a544","tid":1149821,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做得好呀整到支那人唔好黎"},{"pid":"1702ae7b39487cc9a70cf3d0bba19a37299e68d6","tid":1149821,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:06:56.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcde7780e4897c513c908be9bad6b1e6a2265ca6","tid":1149821,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"亲，香港全部都是假貨,打九價還是回內地最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}